BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 12.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 664.00 Tm (Founding principles for peaceful decentralized coordination.) Tj ET
BT 0.330 0.430 0.530 rg /F2 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 643.00 Tm (Public draft) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.90 w 54.00 614.00 m 558.00 614.00 l S
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 594.00 Tm (Founding principles for peaceful decentralized coordination.) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 570.75 Tm (Humanity now possesses the means to communicate, coordinate, and act together across the) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 555.50 Tm (planet.) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 532.25 Tm (We need not wait for kings, parties, corporations, or catastrophes to decide our future. We) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 517.00 Tm (declare these principles.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 484.75 m 558.00 484.75 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 475.75 Tm (I. The People Are the Source) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 443.75 Tm (All legitimate power rises from the people and remains answerable to them.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 411.50 m 558.00 411.50 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 402.50 Tm (II. Consent Above Control) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 370.50 Tm (No authority is just without consent. No consent is real without the freedom to refuse.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 338.25 m 558.00 338.25 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 329.25 Tm (III. Power Must Be Limited) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 297.25 Tm (Any power not checked will drift toward abuse.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 265.00 m 558.00 265.00 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 256.00 Tm (IV. Participation Over Passivity) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 224.00 Tm (Those affected by decisions should have a voice in them.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 191.75 m 558.00 191.75 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 182.75 Tm (V. Decentralize What Can Be Local) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 150.75 Tm (What can be decided locally should never be captured from afar.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 118.50 m 558.00 118.50 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 109.50 Tm (VI. Coordinate What Must Be Shared) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 77.50 Tm (What concerns many may be aligned by many through open cooperation.) Tj ET
