BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 716.00 Tm (VII. Unity Without Uniformity) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 684.00 Tm (People may differ in culture, belief, and way of life while building peace together.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 651.75 m 558.00 651.75 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 642.75 Tm (VIII. Nonviolence Is Strength) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 610.75 Tm (Violence breeds the systems it claims to defeat. Disciplined peace outlasts fear.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 578.50 m 558.00 578.50 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 569.50 Tm (IX. Truth Must Be Visible) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 537.50 Tm (Transparency builds trust. Hidden power corrodes it.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 505.25 m 558.00 505.25 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 496.25 Tm (X. Fatalism Is Folly) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 464.25 Tm (We need not wait for war, collapse, or nuclear fire to become wise.) Tj ET
0.720 0.820 0.900 RG 0.80 w 54.00 432.00 m 558.00 432.00 l S
BT 0.040 0.380 0.620 rg /F2 17 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 423.00 Tm (Closing) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 391.00 Tm (The future is not owned by tyrants, algorithms, or inherited power.) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 367.75 Tm (The future belongs to free peoples who choose to build it together.) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 344.50 Tm (Let assemblies rise wherever people are. Let consent become visible. Let cooperation outrun) Tj ET
BT 0.090 0.160 0.240 rg /F1 10.5 Tf 1 0 0 1 54.00 329.25 Tm (coercion. Let the age of participation begin.) Tj ET
